          <h1>Are you a <span>huge nerd</span>?<br>Did you <span>study STEM</span>?</h1>
        </div>
        <p id="teaching-large-paragraph" class="column xlarge-8 xlarge-pull-4">
          So, you’re a Science, Technology, Engineering or Math (STEM) major?<br>
          Whether you are still studying or recently graduated, we have some cool shit to tell you about. It’s a big f*cking deal.
        </p>
