      <div id="teaching-large-content" class="row">
        <div class="column large-4">
          <div>
            <h3><span>1.</span> I Do Want To Be A STEM Teacher! Can Someone Contact Me With Options?</h3>
            <p>Yeah, We figured that you wanted for us to do the work for you. We made a quick form to fill out. You will reciev an email from the programs that apply to your field of study and location.</p>
            <a class="button blue taller">Have someone contact me</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column large-4">
          <div>
            <h3><span>2.</span> Is There A List of STEM Teaching Programs That Are Available Near Me?</h3>
            <p>There are no dumb questions, especially when they are that good. There is a list, and we have it on this very page!</p>
            <a class="button blue taller">STEM teaching programs</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column large-4">
          <div>
            <h3><span>3.</span> What’s A Teacher? What’s a STEM? Am I Even Good Enough to Teach Our Youth?</h3>
            <p>Whoa dude, whats with the questions? What, am I your teacher? Here are some resources that can answer some of your burning questions. If anything else is burning, please contact a doctor.</p>
            <a class="button blue taller">STEM teaching programs</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
